@base <https://semantic-flow.github.io/sflo/> .
@prefix sflo: <https://semantic-flow.github.io/sflo/ontology/> .

<ontology/ArtifactResolutionFallbackPolicy> sflo:hasReferenceLink <ontology/ArtifactResolutionFallbackPolicy/_knop/_references#reference001> .

